- PyAim Multiplayer -
Made by Pearson Tran
for ICS3U in range (June/13/2023)

Instructions:
1. To play this game, you must first find the IPv4 Address for your client communication.
    1.1 In your command prompt type "ipconfig".
    1.2 Find which wifi network you are connected to.
    1.3 Find the IPv4 Address underneath the network.
        it should start with "192" or "172".
    1.4 Assign your address to the SERVER_IP variable in the constants folder.
2. Run the server file to start accepting communication from clients.
3. Run the clients.
4. Have fun!
NOTE: Each player needs the client file, the game file, the constants file 
and the network file to play. 

